data.description: *BRING YOUR HORSES* 8 ACRES with custom upgraded manufactured home set on patented concrete footer system. Over 1600 sq ft living area, open living design with New  flooring throughout, wood burning fireplace, 4 bedrooms with walk in closets and carpet flooring , 2 bath with En Suite master and garden tub. Freshly installed 12x45 screened patio w insulated roof. ''Timeless'' log cabin style metal siding with insulation, Metal roof and 50 gal water heater. Kinetcio water treatment system and 200 amp electrical service. *WORK* from home in a 30x70 workshop complete with 9000 lb car lift air compressors, 200 amp electrical service, multiple carports and 12X26 enclosed shed. *PLAY* on your own 8 acre paridise with 24 ft pool stocked fish pond, covered boat/RV storage and multiple 50 amp RV hook-ups. Secured with electric entry gate. Country living close to town. 15 min. to New Smyrna Beach, 15 min. to Daytona Speedway, 1 hr. to Orlando.
